OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOften cloudy
OL,6,Fwith further outbreaks of patchy
OL,7,Fdrizzle at first. Strengthening winds
OL,8,Fwill herald a band of heavier rain
OL,9,Flater in the night. Gusty winds
OL,10,Fparticularly near Cardigan Bay coasts
OL,11,Fkeeping the temperatures up overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRain soon clearing to the
OL,14,Feast tomorrow with sunny spells and
OL,15,Fblustery scattered showers following.
OL,16,FThese locally heavy with hail and a
OL,17,Frisk of thunder by the afternoon.
OL,18,FWindier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
