OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FUnsettled on Sunday and Monday with a
OL,7,Fmixture of sunny spells and showers.
OL,8,FSomewhat drier on Tuesday.
OL,9,FTemperatures generally close to
OL,10,Faverage. Breezy at times, especially
OL,11,Faround showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
